@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use the OpenAI Quiz application.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect minimal information to provide the quiz functionality and improve your experience. This includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Quiz Responses:</strong> We collect your quiz answers and selected options only for scoring and result display purposes.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> General usage data, such as the topics and difficulty levels chosen, may be collected to help us improve the quiz content.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To generate, display, and evaluate quiz results.</li>
    <li>To improve quiz questions and enhance user experience.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Disclosure of Your Information</h2>
<p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to third parties except for the purposes of generating quiz content and results via the OpenAI API. The data shared with OpenAI is limited to quiz-related queries and responses necessary for generating the quiz questions.</p>

<h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>Your quiz responses and usage data are stored temporarily and are not retained long-term. We implement security measures to protect your information; however, please be aware that no electronic storage method is entirely secure.</p>

<h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>The OpenAI Quiz application is intended for users of all ages, but if you are under 13, we recommend using the app with parental supervision. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent.</p>

<h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>This application uses OpenAI's API to generate quiz questions based on the topics and difficulty levels you choose. For more information on how OpenAI handles data, please review <a href="https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy" target="_blank">OpenAI's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the effective date at the top will be revised accordingly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy regularly to stay informed about our practices.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled, please contact us at haris97duisburg@gmail.com .</p>
